posts.post_content:
Posted By: Brian McQueen
I spent most of 2007 (and some into 2006) searching for the cards on this list below.  I'm hoping my one final stab at listing my wantlist on BST for the year turns up positive this time.  If I can cross just ONE card off of this list by year's end, that would be terrific and I would be very appreciative.  Any condition is appreciated and I would pay or trade generously for anything below.  Plenty of tradebait available....--


any e94s with orange backgrounds
e100 Cutshaw
1911 Zeenuts - Ryan SF, Halla, Fullerton, Miller, Lindsay, Seaton, Agnew, McKune, Melchoir, and Holland 
1912 Zeenut - Baker
1913 Zeenut - McCarl
1914 Zeenut - Cartwright
t209-2 - BE Thompson, Pressley/Pritchard
any t210 yellow border
t210-3 Morris
t210-7 Kelly Mascot
t213-2 - Murray (KC variation)
t216 - O'Hara or Seigle
